{"tid":1547813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"除左國際戰線外 我求求各公務員再寫聯署信或者集會","createTime":"2019-09-06T20:09:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T03:08:43.000Z","uid":13388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b7f3bcb8f602d5c9417307c96c45b1772adccb43","tid":1547813,"uid":13388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T20:09:30.000Z","msg":"當831 同今日勇武手足既事件後<br />\n我覺得除左要打國際線外<br />\n我地自己香港人都要升級<br />\n沖緊涼時 我一直諗點升級？<br />\n<br />\n就係要再展現比香港人 外國人 <br />\n同埋林奠中共呢個恐殘暴權比佢地知道<br />\n我地香港人對林奠你做埋d下三流既行為<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">絕對唔接受</span><br />\n同埋要證明比大家睇 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地團結一致</span><br />\n<br />\n我記得612 616 618 之後<br />\n有好多公務員都索聯署信同集會 <br />\n表達對五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n所以當林奠所謂既撤回 同恐殘既軍政府<br />\n同埋有傳既打死香港市民<br />\n<br />\n都要重新一次 我地絕對唔會屈服<br />\n<br />\n想係度求求各位公務員 出一出一次聲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非同勇武要團結<br />\n<br />\n利伸 發夢成日係中排食煙既手足上<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"3e33a0dcafd0bfaf3d68e866722b4d4bd8a84bd8","tid":1547813,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T20:09:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一句講晒，睇哩個post</span></span><br />\n[置頂/請廣傳/多圖] 907 遊客LOOK 暢遊大嶼山指南<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1547426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1547426</a>"},{"pid":"a3e2312511a3a08ef13f0a5ab5dce9a8b2a7d516","tid"